---
title: Smart Chicken and Cheddar Patties with Cilantro-Lime Crema and Charred Corn
description: Cheddar and charred corn give these chicken patties a delightful flavour and crispy, golden exterior!  A fresh side salad and a drizzle of cilantro-lime cream over the patties lightens up the plate!
